19 (1) IS AT LEAST 19 YEARS OLD AND UNDER THE AGE OF 65 YEARS;
20 (2) FAILS TO REPORT A CHANGE IN ELIGIBILITY; AND
21 (3) IS NOT:
22 (I) DESIGNATED AS DISABLED BY A GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY;
23 OR
24 (II) PREGNANT.

