1 (E) THE DEPARTMENT SHALL TERMINATE THE ELIGIBILITY OF A PROGRAM
2 RECIPIENT WHO IS SUBJECT TO THE WORK REQUIREMENTS OF THIS SECTION AND
3 FAILS TO COMPLY.
4 (F) BEGINNING MARCH 31, 2027, AND ON A QUARTERLY BASIS
